{
  "stem": "13483.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Thank you, Susie.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, had been killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, when we landed, mostly first the group, the initial landing parties were well-- not well inland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were already a few kilometers inland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I say, I think the Canadians landed the same place as us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was the second Canadian Army landed at the same time as the British troops.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you just saw them, the Canadian and British troops, laying in the sand, dead, or being washed up by the sea and against the beach.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a place called Ver-sur-Mer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first you had go on the beach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to land on the beach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had to take off all your waterproofing equipment, which was on the bulldozer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of the tanks were all waterproofed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you had to prepare your equipment to go forward.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only when we were coming off the LST.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Again, things are a little vague, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A little-- but I remember that once we did land and took the waterproofing equipment off the bulldozers and the equipment, I think we rested a while.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how long for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It couldn't have been very, very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we moved forward, going towards Bayeux.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, from the-- from Arromanches, from beach Arromanches, we went into this place called Ver-sur-Mer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Might've escaped, run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you know, first time I ever saw a civilian, when we went into Bayeux.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this little place, Ver-sur-Mer, was picked out as one of the places where we had to build an airfield.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think the second airfield--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
